wtm.name: Women Tech Makers
wtm.about: Google's Women Techmakers program provides visibility, community, and resources for women in technology.

acm-w.name: ACM-W
acm-w.about: ACM-W supports, celebrates, and advocates internationally for the full engagement of women in all aspects of the computing field, providing a wide range of programs and services to ACM members and working in the larger community to advance the contributions of technical women.

wics.name: Women in CyberSecurity
wics.about: Women in CyberSecurity works to recruit, retain, and advance women in cybersecurity.

swe.name: Society of Women Engineers
swe.about: SWE encourages women to achieve full potential in careers as engineers and leaders.

ncwit.name: National Center for Women in Technology
ncwit.about: NCWIT is a national non-profit focused on women's participation in computing across the entire ecosystem
